OL,3,CPSNI officer's decision to use lethal
OL,4,Cforce in shooting 'proportionate'
OL,6,FA PSNI officer's decision to use
OL,7,Flethal force after a stolen car failed
OL,8,Fto stop at a checkpoint almost 18
OL,9,Fyears ago was "proportionate", a
OL,10,Fcoroner has found.
OL,12,FSteven Colwell, 23, originally from
OL,13,FBelfast, died on Easter Sunday 2006
OL,14,Fafter police fired at the stolen BMW
OL,15,Fhe was driving which failed to stop at
OL,16,Fthe checkpoint in Ballynahinch, Co
OL,17,FDown.
