OL,3,CPSNI officer's decision to use lethal
OL,4,Cforce in shooting 'proportionate'
OL,6,FThe officer responsible, identified
OL,7,Fonly as Officer O during the inquest,
OL,8,Ffired two shots into the car after it
OL,9,Fengaged in dangerous driving
OL,10,Fmanoeuvres at a vehicle checkpoint.
OL,12,FJudge Neil Rafferty, acting as
OL,13,Fcoroner, said the officer had a
OL,14,Freasonable belief that there was a
OL,15,Fthreat to his life and the lives of
OL,16,Fothers.
OL,18,FHe said: "The force used by the
OL,19,Fofficer was no more than was
OL,20,Fabsolutely necessary."
