OL,6,FThe inquest heard that there were five
OL,7,Fpassengers in the vehicle with Mr
OL,8,FColwell, four of whom were in the back
OL,9,Fseat.
OL,11,FThe coroner said that the occupants of
OL,12,Fthe stolen BMW were a "chaotic group
OL,13,Fof young people" under the influence
OL,14,Fof alcohol and, in most cases, drugs.
