OL,6,FAfter detailing evidence relating to a
OL,7,Fparty and an altercation following an
OL,8,Fattempted burglary prior to the
OL,9,Fshooting, the coroner said the young
OL,10,Fpeople had been "running amok" in the
OL,11,Fcar driven by Mr Colwell, who
OL,12,Ftoxicology reports found was likely to
OL,13,Fhave been severely impaired by ecstasy.
OL,15,FThe levels of MDMA in Mr Colwell's
OL,16,Fsystem were described as much higher
OL,17,Fthan usually associated with
OL,18,Frecreational use and fell within the
OL,19,Frange found in fatal poisonings.
