OL,3,CPSNI officer's decision to use lethal
OL,4,Cforce in shooting 'proportionate'
OL,6,FThe coroner said the officers at
OL,7,FBallynahinch had a lack of information
OL,8,Frequired to bring the vehicle to a
OL,9,Fstop and arrest the occupants.
OL,11,FHe said their "undeveloped plan" was
OL,12,Fconceptually flawed and tactically
OL,13,Finappropriate, and seems to have been
OL,14,Fbased on erroneous information that
OL,15,Fthe driver was not likely to attempt
OL,16,Fto evade the stop.
