OL,4,Cforce in shooting 'proportionate'
OL,6,FHe said Officer O and a constable who
OL,7,Fwas also involved in the stop were
OL,8,Ftaken by surprise when the vehicle
OL,9,Fattempted to avoid the checkpoint and
OL,10,Fstarted conducting dangerous driving
OL,11,Fmanoeuvres.
OL,13,FOfficer O, who was the senior officer
OL,14,Fon the team at the checkpoint,
OL,15,Fattempted a "hard or firm stop".
OL,17,FThis typically involves pointing a
OL,18,Fweapon at a suspect and informing them
OL,19,Fthey are dealing with armed officers
OL,20,Fprepared to shoot.
