OL,4,Cforce in shooting 'proportionate'
OL,6,FThe coroner said Officer O made clear
OL,7,Fand loud instructions to stop but did
OL,8,Fnot find that he had informed Mr
OL,9,FColwell he was armed or prepared to
OL,10,Fshoot his Glock pistol.
OL,12,FHe said Mr Colwell had a "clear
OL,13,Fdetermination" to drive away
OL,14,Firrespective of what dangers he was
OL,15,Fcausing.
OL,17,FJudge Rafferty added: "I find the
OL,18,Fdanger was real.
