OL,6,F"The coroner said he was not satisfied
OL,7,Fthat Officer O had positioned himself
OL,8,Fin front of the vehicle deliberately,
OL,9,Fadding "several things were happening
OL,10,Fat the same time" including the BMW
OL,11,Fcolliding with a Ford Mondeo.
OL,13,FHe said Officer O did not have a
OL,14,Fviable or realistic avenue or option
OL,15,Fof retreat when the BMW then
OL,16,Faccelerated forward.
