OL,3,CPSNI officer's decision to use lethal
OL,4,Cforce in shooting 'proportionate'
OL,6,FHe said Officer O was not unreasonable
OL,7,Fto believe the BMW was coming straight
OL,8,Fat him and that it would have been
OL,9,Funreasonable for him to have checked
OL,10,Fthe direction of the tyres, which were
OL,11,Fpre-set for a lefthand steer, in the
OL,12,Fsplit second time frame.
OL,14,FThe coroner said, on the balance of
OL,15,Fprobabilities, he could not be aware
OL,16,Fthe vehicle would sharply turn left.
OL,18,FIt was therefore a reasonable mistake
OL,19,Fto believe the vehicle was coming
OL,20,Fstraight for him.
