OL,6,FHowever, in his conclusions, the judge
OL,7,Fsaid the PSNI had failed to provide a
OL,8,Fsatisfactory or convincing explanation
OL,9,Fthat the operation had been planned
OL,10,Fand controlled with care to minimise
OL,11,Fthe risk to life.
OL,13,FHe said obvious control and planning
OL,14,Fimprovements could have improved the
OL,15,Fprospects of the tragic events being
OL,16,Favoided.
OL,18,FHe said a call from a witness about
OL,19,Fthe vehicle was "inappropriately
OL,20,Fhandled" and vital information was
OL,21,Fmissed.
