OL,6,FA separate investigation into the
OL,7,Fincident was previously carried out by
OL,8,Fthe Police Ombudsman.
OL,10,FThen-ombudsman Al Hutchinson found in
OL,11,Fhis report in 2011 that the actions of
OL,12,Fa policeman in shooting dead the
OL,13,Fdriver of a stolen car were
OL,14,F"critically flawed".
OL,16,FSpeaking outside Belfast Coroner's
OL,17,FCourt, Mr Colwell's brother expressed
OL,18,Fdisappointment with the inquest
OL,19,Ffindings.
