OL,6,FNeil Colwell said the family were glad
OL,7,Fto see the end of the "long haul"
OL,8,Finquest, which had its first hearing
OL,9,Fin 2017.
OL,11,FHe said he felt that if the PSNI "had
OL,12,Fmanaged their response better" his
OL,13,Fbrother might have been alive today.
OL,15,FSolicitor Padraig O'Muirigh, who
OL,16,Frepresents the family, said they
OL,17,Fintend to consider potential future
OL,18,Fsteps."
